  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-39ed6ac2-7fff-0ec4-63cc-ed9f915f95ae&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;The proposed development, by virtue of its design, scale, form, and location, would be an unsympathetic addition to the property that is out of keeping with surrounding development and that fails to preserve or enhance the character and appearance of the conservation area. The proposal is, therefore, contrary to policies D4 and HC1 of the London Plan (2021) and policies LP1 and LP3 of Hackney Local Plan (2020), and Hackney&#x27;s Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD (2009). &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
